Project

Building an open data project for the city of Antibes, France to promote the publication of higher quality datasets. The project includes:

  • Github repository
  • Website
  • Contributions to the data.gouv.fr platform

Learnings

Learnings include problem solving, visual communication and technical knowledge:

  • Data wrangling
  • Data visualization
  • Versioning : Git and Github
  • Static reporing framework (html rendering)
